# NASA Data

This folder contains the original multiband HLS imagery and training points provided in the NASA course example for LCLU classification.  
- **HLS_2017_multiband.tif** – Multiband imagery for 2017  
- **HLS_2024_multiband.tif** – Multiband imagery for 2024  
- **training_points_2017.gpkg** – Training points for 2017 used to build the Random Forest model  

These files are included to reproduce the classification workflow and support the Shiny app development.

